# Jackson-core DoS vulnerabilities - managed by Spring Boot 4.0.3 BOM
# Cannot upgrade without Spring Boot upgrade. Both are DoS (not RCE/data leak).
# Revisit when Spring Boot 4.1.x ships with Jackson 2.21.x / 3.1.x
