# Go stdlib CVEs in Paketo lifecycle launcher binary (buildpacksio/lifecycle 0.21.5, Go 1.26.0)
# Not in our app code - lifecycle launcher is build-time infrastructure embedded in image layers.
# Cannot upgrade independently - managed by Paketo builder. Fixed in Go 1.26.1.
# Revisit when paketobuildpacks/ubuntu-noble-builder ships lifecycle built with Go 1.26.1+
